column5:
Hi I just wanted to tell you about how this movement is helping people in different ways. Our discord server and movement is made to help people that are dealing with different struggles in life. We cover a wide variety of life issues and that list is always growing. We find and present the best information and tools for people to use that we believe can change their lives in many different ways.

If you would like to join our community please message me.
I went through this and then I did an online school and it changed my life

I went though something very similar with my mum, I then left home for 9 months and then I moved back in with my mum and we are now our mother son relationship is better than it's ever been. Try talking to you mum about the issues you have bought up and we are always here if you need advice

There is a way of life for everyone. There is a reason you are alive. The best thing to do would be try find someone with training that can help you with your depression and problems. We are always here to chat if you need advice my friend.
I couldn't agree with you more
